OL,3,CRise in national insurance to hit jobs
OL,4,Cand investment, high street bosses warn
OL,6,FHigh street jobs and investment plans
OL,7,Fare at risk because of the hike in
OL,8,Fnational insurance payments, retail
OL,9,Fand hospitality bosses have warned.
OL,11,FIt comes as the rate of employer NICs
OL,12,F(national insurance contributions)
OL,13,Fincreases from 13.8% to 15% on Sunday
OL,14,FApril 6.
OL,16,FAt the same time, firms will also pay
OL,17,Fmore because the Government lowered
OL,18,Fthe salary threshold at which
OL,19,Fcompanies start paying NICs from
OL,20,F#9,100 to #5,000.
