OL,3,CRise in national insurance to hit jobs
OL,4,Cand investment, high street bosses warn
OL,6,FUK retailers have warned that hiring
OL,7,Fplans, particularly for part-time
OL,8,Fworkers, will be held back as a result.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, the boss of one of the UK's
OL,11,Flargest pub groups said he was
OL,12,F"trimming" some investment plans to
OL,13,Fdeal with the surge in costs.
OL,15,FThe fresh tax increase comes days
OL,16,Fafter businesses were hit by a 6.7%
OL,17,Fincrease in the national minimum wage.
