OL,3,CRise in national insurance to hit jobs
OL,4,Cand investment, high street bosses warn
OL,6,FMany high street firms have also faced
OL,7,Fhigher costs from an increase in
OL,8,Fbusiness rates due to a reduction in
OL,9,Fcurrent discounts for more than
OL,10,F250,000 retail, hospitality and
OL,11,Fleisure firms.
OL,13,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC)
OL,14,Fsaid changes to NICs and wages will
OL,15,Fcost retailers another #5 billion over
OL,16,Fthe next year.
OL,18,FIt said it will cost shops 10% more to
OL,19,Femploy workers due to the changes, and
OL,20,F13% higher for part-time staff.
