OL,3,CRise in national insurance to hit jobs
OL,4,Cand investment, high street bosses warn
OL,6,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe BRC, said: "A recent survey of
OL,8,Fretail finance directors showed that
OL,9,Fhalf were planning to reduce hours and
OL,10,Fworkers as a direct result of the
OL,11,Femployer NIC hike.
OL,13,F"It will be part-time jobs which take
OL,14,Fthe biggest hit.
OL,16,F"Part-time retail jobs hit their
OL,17,Flowest level since records began in
OL,18,F1996, and have fallen by 200,000 in
OL,19,Fthe last seven years.
